{"tid":2196083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"NGO鬼話篇：香港小童群益會 Blame the victim","createTime":"2020-09-09T15:05:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-11T10:27:09.000Z","uid":186,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"25b82dda9fcdbdbb339d95db023adc939a63a83e","tid":2196083,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T15:05:08.000Z","msg":"【就一名女童於9月6日在旺角街頭被警察制服事宜之回應】<br />\n<br />\n九月六日十二歲女童在旺角居所附近，在混亂環境中奔跑被警務人員制服，受到驚嚇和損傷的事件，香港小童群益會表示關注。我們期望當局能透過公正可靠具透明度的調查，釐清事實。<br />\n<br />\n本會認為，執法人員身經專業培訓，面對兒童對象，執行行動時須考慮現場環境、盡力保障兒童權利，嚴格遵行特區政府簽訂的《兒童權利公約》，避免兒童受到傷害。我們亦在此呼籲，<span class=\"red\">兒童應遠離暴力和衝突現場，以策安全。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/101795399863547/posts/3516589901717396/?extid=MMxj212PsnxWqCLM&amp;d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F101795399863547%2Fposts%2F3516589901717396%2F%3Fextid%3DMMxj212PsnxWqCLM%26d%3Dn&d=8aZ3B%2FsgtJclBbEiVdGGE5S3ibws79Cb3MvuL7akqOg%3D&h=ac4a226b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/101795399863547/posts/3516589901717396/?extid=MMxj212PsnxWqCLM&amp;d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xamg9WO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxamg9WO.png&h=9f0aa93f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"221b999696d0045b155eae783bd9ab1ad6bc9b10","tid":2196083,"uid":186,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T15:05:50.000Z","msg":"不如改名叫 <strong><del>The Boys&rsquo; and Girls&rsquo;</del> Blame the Girl Clubs Association of Hong Kong</strong><br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">Blame Girl Clubs Association</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\nBGCA<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b01f353ce9ec647e83508607a6052991f45173","tid":2196083,"uid":133033,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime